@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About the Project";
    ViewBag.Message = "Learn more about the Training Management System.";
}
<main aria-labelledby="title" class="container mt-5">
    <h2 id="title" class="text-primary mb-4">@ViewBag.Title</h2>
    <h3 class="text-secondary mb-4">@ViewBag.Message</h3>

    <section class="bg-light p-4 rounded">
        <h4 class="text-dark">Project Overview</h4>
        <p class="lead">
            The Training Management System is a web application built with ASP.NET MVC and Entity Framework.
            It streamlines the training process at a university by managing interactions between students,
            university supervisors, and administrative staff. The system provides a platform for students to
            upload reports, supervisors to review and provide feedback, and admins to manage users and oversee
            the entire process.
        </p>

        <h4 class="text-dark mt-4">Key Features</h4>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>User Management:</strong> Admins can manage users (students, supervisors, trainers) and oversee the system.
                Supervisors review and provide feedback on reports, while students submit reports and view feedback.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Dashboards:</strong> Students and supervisors have personalized dashboards for managing reports and communication.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Feedback System:</strong> Supervisors can approve or reject reports with optional feedback.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Authentication:</strong> Secure login with role-based access ensures users see only relevant features.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Validation:</strong> Includes rules for user input, such as complex passwords for supervisors.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-4">
            The system aims to enhance the efficiency and transparency of the training process, providing a user-friendly interface
            for all involved parties.
        </p>
    </section>
</main>

<!-- Add some custom CSS to further enhance the look -->
<style>
    .container {
        max-width: 800px;
    }

    .bg-light {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }

    .text-primary {
        color: #007bff;
    }

    .text-secondary {
        color: #6c757d;
    }

    .text-dark {
        color: #343a40;
    }

    .lead {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 300;
    }

    .list-group-item {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        padding: 10px 15px;
    }

    .rounded {
        border-radius: .25rem;
    }

    .mt-4 {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
</style>
